  "body": "R. Hamburg (UAH) reports on behalf of the Fermi Gamma-ray Burst Monitor\nTeam:\n\n���The Fermi Gamma-ray Burst Monitor (GBM) trigger\n220331776/670444627 at 18:37:02.27 UT on\n31 March 2022, tentatively classified as a\nGRB (GCN 31808), is in fact not due to a GRB.\nThis trigger is due to a solar flare.���"
